        "minor": [
          {
            "comment": "chore(refine): improve refine headless module: fix dead labelPlacement option, use RefineConfigError in createOptionList, consolidate visually-hidden CSS, unify disabled option convention across headless primitives to Readable signals, split SwipeControl onCancel/onRelease, add selection-control/spinner test coverage",
